				<li class="text">AI & Machine Learning for Beginners</li>
				<li class="text">
					Digital Skills for Diplomats, NGOs, & Governement Agencies.
				</li>
				<li class="text">
					Practical IT Workshops for Senior Professionals
				</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
